title: Snarf # 1-15 (Kitchen Sink)
description:
Issue five is misssing here

15 issues comix anthology published by Kitchen Sink between 1972 and 1990. The publishing shedule seemed pretty random sometimes with almost 10 years passing between two issues. The series became a venue for a handful of notable North American and Canadian talents. It also featured re-prints and imported talents.

Contributors included:
